:<font size="15">יין</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
יין / yayin / yah'-yin

===Etymology===
From an unused root meaning to effervesce; 

===Noun===
'''יין'''

# wine (as fermented); by implication intoxication: - banqueting, wine, wine [-bibber].

